zh_cn.telemetry.event.performance_metrics.desc:
了解Minecraft的整体性能概况，可以帮助我们针对各种机型和操作系统调整与优化游戏。 
游戏版本信息也包含在其中，以帮助我们比较Minecraft新版本的性能概况。
zh_cn.telemetry.event.world_load_times.descrip: 对我们而言，了解加入世界所需的时长，以及这一时长随着时间推移会如何变化是很重要的。比如，当我们加入新功能或进行较大的技术更改时，我们需要知道这对加载时间有何影响。
zh_cn.telemetry.event.world_load_times.title: 世界加载时间
zh_cn.telemetry.event.world_loaded.description:
了解玩家玩Minecraft时的具体细节（例如游戏模式、客户端或服务端是否被修改，以及游戏版本）能够帮助我们专注于游戏更新以改进玩家最关心的部分。
世界加载事件将同世界卸载事件一起用于计算游戏会话的持续时长。
zh_cn.telemetry.event.world_loaded.title: 世界加载
zh_cn.telemetry.event.world_unloaded.descripti:
此事件与世界加载事件用于计算世界会话的持续时间。
持续时间（以秒和刻为单位）在世界会话结束时（退回到标题屏幕，或从服务器断开连接）测量。

en_us.telemetry_info.opt_in.description: I consent to sending optional telemetry data
en_us.telemetry_info.screen.description:
Collecting this data helps us improve Minecraft by guiding us in directions that are relevant to our players.
You can also send in additional feedback to help us keep improving Minecraft.
en_us.telemetry_info.screen.title: Telemetry Data Collection
en_us.telemetry.event.advancement_made.descrip: Understanding the context behind receiving an advancement can help us better understand and improve the progression of the game.
en_us.telemetry.event.advancement_made.title: Advancement Made
en_us.telemetry.event.game_load_times.descript: This event can help us figure out where startup performance improvements are needed by measuring the execution times of the startup phases.
en_us.telemetry.event.game_load_times.title: Game Load Times
en_us.telemetry.event.performance_metrics.desc:
Knowing the overall performance profile of Minecraft helps us tune and optimize the game for a wide range of machine specifications and operating systems. 
Game version is included to help us compare the performance profile for new versions of Minecraft.
en_us.telemetry.event.world_load_times.descrip: It’s important for us to understand how long it takes to join a world, and how that changes over time. For example, when we add new features or do larger technical changes, we need to see what impact that had on load times.
en_us.telemetry.event.world_load_times.title: World Load Times
en_us.telemetry.event.world_loaded.description:
Knowing how players play Minecraft (such as Game Mode, client or server modded, and game version) allows us to focus game updates to improve the areas that players care about most.
The World Loaded event is paired with the World Unloaded event to calculate how long the play session has lasted.
en_us.telemetry.event.world_loaded.title: World Loaded
en_us.telemetry.event.world_unloaded.descripti:
This event is paired with the World Loaded event to calculate how long the world session has lasted.
The duration (in seconds and ticks) is measured when a world session has ended (quitting to title, disconnecting from a server).
en_us.telemetry.event.world_unloaded.title: World Unloaded
